            <title>[HADOOP-6404] Rename the generated artifacts to common instead of core</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-6404</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the project split we renamed Core to Common, but failed to change the artifact names. We should do it before 0.21.0 is released.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
